      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It handles beautifully and looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a reliable car that still has plenty of adventures left in it, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
