    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2015 Land Cruiser is a robust example of legendary engineering, maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior shines in Midnight Black; while there are minor road-pebbles on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper, the paint remains deep and reflective. Inside, the parchment leather interior is remarkably clean, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster and no cracks or tears. Mechanically, this SUV is turn-key. The V8 engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts imperceptibly. Recent service includes a full synthetic oil change, a brake fluid flush, and a fresh set of Michelin Defender tires. All electronics, including the multi-zone climate control and the premium audio system, function perfectly. It drives straight, brakes firm, and offers the composed ride quality these vehicles are known for. Includes two keys and a comprehensive folder of service records.",
